                    <p>Creators report up to 10x increase in PPV sales and 5x more tips using our AI chat assistant.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Super Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p>Simple Chrome extension setup with one-click response generation that sounds exactly like you.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Customizable Persona</h3>
                    <p>Choose from multiple persona templates or create your own unique voice to match your brand.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Works With Your Platforms</h3>
                    <p>Seamlessly integrates with top creator platforms to help you manage all your fan communications.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>24/7 Fan Engagement</h3>
                    <p>Never miss a message again - our AI responds even when you're asleep or busy creating content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
