                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p>"Our agency uses AICreatorChat for multiple clients now. It's incredibly user-friendly and we've seen revenue increase for every creator within the first month."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">Michael, Agency Owner</div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p>"I was drowning in messages and losing subscribers because I couldn't keep up. This AI tool saved my business and has doubled my income."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">@stellarcreator</div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p>"The AI responses are so natural that my fans can't tell the difference. I've been able to scale my content creation while maintaining personal connections."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">Alex, Fitness Creator</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to 10x Your Creator Income?</h2>
            <p>Join thousands of creators already using AICreatorChat</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Get Started For Free</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 AICreatorChat. All rights reserved.</p>
